tras/4ed7acc11ec8b638370660dce5340391.poster.avif?t=1728112351\" width=440 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1519850/extras/4ed7acc11ec8b638370660dce5340391.webm?t=1728112351\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1519850/extras/4ed7acc11ec8b638370660dce5340391.mp4?t=1728112351\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Key Features:</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fast-paced reaction gameplay with increasing difficulty</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Simple one-button control: stop at the right time to avoid obstacles</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Variety of enemies, lasers, spikes, and boost cubes to navigate</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Online leaderboards and medal rewards for each level</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Engaging and challenging levels for quick but intense sessions</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Are you ready to put your reflexes to the test and dominate the leaderboards?</p>",
